/******* FRACT'OL MANUAL *******\

Weclome to fract'ol !

Available fractals : mandlebrot, julia, burning ship and mandlebrot with z^3
Launch with : ./fractol fractal_name [mandle|julia|bship|mandle3] (optional:win_width)

Moving : Arrows
Zooming : Mouse wheel
R,G,B values : T,Y,U keys for + and G,H,J for -
Reset : R
Next fractal : C
Julia set modifier : Mouse motion
Switch UI : Tab
Switch "follow cursor" : Z
Switch julia set modifier lock : Mouse left button

Enjoy fractals :) !
